      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# Nxdify Image Generation Node - Quick Guide\n\n## Overview\n\nGenerates image variations using FAL AI Seedream 4.5 with 4 reference images (Face, Body, Breasts, Dynamic Pose).\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- **FAL AI API key** from https://fal.ai/dashboard\n\n## Inputs\n\n- **Face Image**: Reference for face features\n- **Body Image**: Reference for body shape\n- **Breasts Image**: Reference for breasts\n- **Dynamic Pose Image**: Determines Nxdified output pose\n- **Prompt**: Text description of desired output\n- **FAL API Key**: Your FAL AI API key (hidden input)\n- **Quality**: `auto_4K` (default) or `auto_2K`\n\n## Outputs\n\n- **Image**: Generated image in ComfyUI format\n\n## Usage\n\n1. Load 4 reference images into blue group\n2. Enter FAL API Key\n3. Run workflow\n\n## Tips\n\n- Use clear, well-lit reference images\n- Face image should be front-facing\n- Dynamic Pose image changes the output pose\n- First 3 images are cached after upload (faster on repeat)\n- Generation typically takes 40-60 seconds\n\n## Troubleshooting\n\n- **\"API key required\"**: Enter valid FAL API key\n- **\"Upload timeout\"**: Resize images smaller or check connection\n- **\"No images returned\"**: Check prompt or API credits\n- **Long wait times**: Normal (40-60s), check console logs with `[Nxdify]` prefix\n"
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
